# Portal-elected admins. Managed by the /admin/users UI.
# One email per line. Unioned with ADMIN_GROUP_OID and ADMIN_USERS env —
# any one of the three signals makes a user admin.
#
# Caddy never reads this file. The portal exposes it for cross-user
# admin actions (workspace lifecycle, terminal, container logs, port
# proxy) via /internal/check-admin which Caddy hits as a forward_auth
# subrequest before letting the request reach the workspace container.
